OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1784035119
OL,3,CTwo arrested after an attempted ATM
OL,4,Ctheft in south Belfast
OL,6,FA man and a woman have been arrested
OL,7,Ffollowing an attempted ATM theft in
OL,8,Fsouth Belfast.
OL,10,FThe man, aged in his 50s, and woman in
OL,11,Fher 40s, were arrested on suspicion of
OL,12,Fa number of offences following the
OL,13,Fincident in Finaghy in the early hours
OL,14,Fof Monday.
OL,16,FA police spokesperson said they
OL,17,Freceived a report shortly after 4am
OL,18,Fthat an attempt had been made to gain
OL,19,Faccess to an ATM in the Upper Lisburn
OL,20,FRoad area.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/4
