OL,3,CTwo arrested after an attempted ATM
OL,4,Ctheft in south Belfast
OL,6,F"Damage was noted to the ATM, but
OL,7,Fnothing was taken," they said.
OL,9,F"A man, aged in his 50s, and a woman
OL,10,Faged in her 40s have been arrested on
OL,11,Fsuspicion of a number of offences
OL,12,Fincluding attempted burglary, going
OL,13,Fequipped for burglary and drugs
OL,14,Foffences. They both remain in custody
OL,15,Fat this time.
