OL,3,CTwo arrested after an attempted ATM
OL,4,Ctheft in south Belfast
OL,6,F"An investigation is under way and
OL,7,Fanyone who witnessed suspicious
OL,8,Factivity in the Upper Lisburn Road
OL,9,Farea in the early hours of Monday
OL,10,Fmorning, or who may have CCTV, dash-
OL,11,Fcam or other footage, is asked to
OL,12,Fcontact police using our witness
OL,13,Fappeal form at https:/
OL,14,F/reporting.psni.police.uk/appeals
OL,15,Fquoting 280 of 13/07/26 or call us on
OL,16,F101."
